(1, 1, '2015-03-21 20:34:51', '2015-03-21 20:34:51', 'This theme has been built based on open source administration system Wordpress and AIT framework, which contain AIT page builder with elements - custom post types and plugins options. The theme admin section is divided into 4 fully customizable parts: Theme options, Default layout, Page Builder, Import / Export. Elements are available below Theme Admin options. You can manage from there all theme custom post types and features provided by elements which are ready to use in the theme.\r\n\r\nWorking with theme is easy as following steps:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Create as many as you need pages in section Pages</li>\r\n	<li>Go to Page builder and select Page you wish to customize</li>\r\n	<li>Write elements content</li>\r\n	<li>Define page layout by drag and drop operations</li>\r\n	<li>Set up parameters of elements</li>\r\n	<li>Repeat previous steps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Enjoy your free time. Focus your energy for creativity. We aimed to save your money.</h3>\r\n[gallery link="file" columns="4" ids="3051,3057,3071,3058"]', 'Build your own website easily', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'build-your-own-website-easily', '', '', '2015-07-08 21:13:44', '2015-07-08 21:13:44', '', 0, 'http://autoskoly.dev/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
